org.apache.flink.runtime.blob

类 BlobCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.blob.BlobCache
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    BlobService

    public final class BlobCache
extends Object
implements BlobService
    The BLOB cache implements a local cache for content-addressable BLOBs. When requesting BLOBs through the getURL(org.apache.flink.runtime.blob.BlobKey) methods, the BLOB cache will first attempt serve the file from its local cache. Only if the local cache does not contain the desired BLOB, the BLOB cache will try to download it from the BLOB server.

      • getURL

        public URL getURL(BlobKey requiredBlob)
           throws IOException
        Returns the URL for the BLOB with the given key. The method will first attempt to serve the BLOB from its local cache. If the BLOB is not in the cache, the method will try to download it from this cache's BLOB server.
        指定者:
        getURL 在接口中 BlobService
        参数:
        requiredBlob - The key of the desired BLOB.
        返回:
        URL referring to the local storage location of the BLOB.
        抛出:
        IOException - Thrown if an I/O error occurs while downloading the BLOBs from the BLOB server.
